Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\pos(331,320)}{\fnArial Black\pos(197.5,203.125)\fad(300,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:44.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.89,0:00:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.22,0:01:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Deck Master:\N Judge Man's Judgment"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.02,0:01:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting Yugi Mutou aside...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he would be defeated by that amateur girl, when she barely knows how to Duel…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a useless bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah-{\i0}sama{\i1}, you were right. We deserve punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.75,0:01:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ouka, is it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.96,0:02:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t get the wrong idea.\N I’m not really all that angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.18,0:02:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being one of the Big Five, the group that betrayed the Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, I was planning to put you to work as my chess pieces, but I guess that isn’t happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.91,0:02:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have any use for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.08,0:02:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may as well\N give up on getting a body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.32,0:02:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}H-Hold on Noah-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.03,0:02:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, out of the Big Five, those two are the most useless idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I am completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you give me one more chance, I will meet your expectations, Noah-{\i0}sama{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You’re pretty confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.75,0:02:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, when I am\N done beating these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.92,0:02:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}will you please\N grant me with a new body?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.40,0:02:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Leave this to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tricky bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.98,0:03:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I’ll let him do as he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you guys are only responsible for getting rid of the small fry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick any weakling\N you want to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the man that\N I'm {\i1}really{\i0} interested in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Ship, do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle Ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I guess it won’t work, big brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.42,0:03:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose we’ll have to get out of this annoying Virtual Space first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Shizuka! Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, I’ve been separated from everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those Big Five old bastards aren’t in sight, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.51,0:03:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can’t just laze around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:03:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A door behind the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.09,0:04:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}suspicious{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.45,0:04:10.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh! That’s the Battle Ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.91,0:04:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I’m out to the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.32,0:04:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe everyone’s made it back already?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.31,0:04:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yugi, Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange, nobody's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that room…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I plan on letting you enjoy the inside of the world in your mind to the {\b0}fullest{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Mai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely defeat Malik so that you'll be able to wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.60,0:05:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.51,0:05:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that you're still in our Virtual World.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am {\i1}so{\i0} sorry to have lied to you, Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.60,0:05:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one of the Big Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I waited to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.08,0:05:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I am one of the Big 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a lawyer for Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.26,0:05:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Ouka Chikuzen.\N Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're a lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a man capable of turning black into white, so long as it benefits Kaiba Corporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you can say that because of me, Kaiba Corporation has became such a big industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You can turn black into white?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have to pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:06:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that comparison was a tad bit too difficult for you to comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, regardless of what our company is charged with,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so long as I am in on the lawsuit, the end result will charge the suer is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.55,0:06:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could that make you feel so proud?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lawyer's job should be to tell the {\i1}truth{\i0} to everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.90,0:06:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me ask you then, what exactly is ''the truth''?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the truth means you have real facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I guess my question was a little too difficult for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let me teach you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.84,0:06:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is whatever my legal argument says it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.30,0:06:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about different things here!\N You're really pissing me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.11,0:06:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lying trickster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, you're here to Duel me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you {\i1}sure{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose, I'll take your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stuff like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.23,0:07:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to escape from this Virtual World, I gotta {\i1}beat you{\i0}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Then let us begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.51,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be our Duel Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.43,0:07:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are we {\i1}now{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see, we are in the Grand Court Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.62,0:07:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the Judge and\N you are the accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.45,0:07:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the accused?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am usually the defender of the accused person,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but today I will\N be making an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall deliver to you your judgment, acting as Judge Man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge Man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just keep changing forms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.88,0:07:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you just had to\N pose as {\b0}Mai{\b1} before...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You made me think\N she was really waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now will the accused, Katsuya Jounouchi, please build yourself a deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good... this one and this one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.31,0:08:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.47,0:08:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Katsuya Jounouchi, I'm predicting you'll be playing a "Gamble Deck".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judge, I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, now you pick one of those cards to serve as your Deck Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right. Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Flame Swordsman?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.36,0:08:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been fighting beside this guy for a long time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a Monster I can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This guy should be just right to be my Deck Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master is the Flame Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Flame Swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell me what your ability is as my Deck Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master Ability allows me to slash my own Attack Power by intervals of 100,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and add them to another Warrior-Type Monster's Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.61,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you can see,\N my Deck Master is Judge Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is now time\N to begin our Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.30,0:09:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.99,0:09:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Hysterical Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Monster really pisses me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1800 Attack Points, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep her in Attack Mode\N and finish this turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.65,0:09:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes {\i1}my{\i0} turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Iron Knight Gearfried...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It has the same amount of Attack Points as his Monster, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good! Time to use\N my Deck Master's Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Iron Knight Gearfried!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also use use my Deck Master Ability to raise his Attack Points by 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.76,0:10:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes! Iron Knight Gearfried, attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.85,0:10:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill the Hysterical Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You used your\N Deck Master Ability so soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.45,0:10:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You learned the rules faster than I anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.87,0:10:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.88,0:10:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.20,0:10:39.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a Monster in Reverse\N and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He probably set a Monster with a Reverse Effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.92,0:10:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But Master Jounouchi\N don't fear nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.57,0:10:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just keep playing carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Little-Winguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use my Deck Master Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.57,0:11:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I increase his Attack Power\N by 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Little-Winguard to attack your Reverse Monster Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Reverse Effect\N of Helping Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get to draw another card.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I got rid of your Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.09,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes. I'll use Gearfried to Direct Attack you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You have remarkable skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? You finally understand how great my skills are?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:40.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At your current level, you cannot beat me no matter how hard you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on and smirk all you want!\N You still can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enjoy your arrogance\N while you still can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Letting your enemy get caught up with success is my gambling theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.43,0:11:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.97,0:12:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This way I can make you wait longer and you'll be too shocked to relax and think straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.95,0:12:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Holy Elf\N in Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll cover another card\N to finish this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.79,0:12:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playtime has long past!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.28,0:12:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm about to get serious with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the others\N are doing alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm sure they'll\N also be forced to Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.27,0:12:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Jounouch-{\i1}kun{\i0} will be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:13:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0}'s and Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s amateur Dueling skills that worries me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.38,0:13:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honda has no talent\N in Dueling whatsoever!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.74,0:13:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, it's not serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} your cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}not{\i0} a cold!\N Someone's just talking about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, and I don't think that Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} understands the rules of Dueling yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! She caught it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stay away from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.03,0:13:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's {\i1}with{\i0} you, Otogi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I'll spread it to {\i1}you{\i0} too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just knock it off, will ya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't hurry and find them soon, Shizuka-{\i1}chan{\i0} and the guys will be in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.97,0:13:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, where does this forest lead to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.56,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you, Noah...\N Just you {\i1}wait{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.53,0:13:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will escape from this ridiculous Virtual World and show you who's boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want out of that forest so bad, I'll let you have your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:11.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The President's office\N at Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.44,0:14:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Gozaburo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.49,0:14:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I want to talk with you about the Virtual System I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, these are Virtual Images as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.47,0:14:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened two years before I became the president of Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you want,\N I have nothing to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.24,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto... I'm busy now,\N so please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.68,0:14:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invented that system so everyone could enjoy {\i1}games{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Father, you want to use it for war!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said get out.\N Didn't you {\i1}hear{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system is not a war tool!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invented it for people to use in the future Kaiba Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said get out already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What Kaiba Land?!\N Hmph! It's all nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.37,0:15:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such ridiculous games\N have no use for man!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen very carefully, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever inherits Kaiba Corporation must make things that are of great use to mankind around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.56,0:15:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I myself must dominate the world with my military business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to use the Virtual System you developed to reproduce the territory of world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.65,0:15:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're {\i1}wrong{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me. Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.33,0:15:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the last day I addressed that man as my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was willing to let countless numbers of people die in wars with the Virtual System just so he could make a fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.45,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't hand it over to that evil man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.75,0:16:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that day, I totally lost my respect for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I made up my mind that Kaiba Corporation would belong to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of that... it's unforgivable to go into our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.07,0:16:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and secretly watch our reactions and make fun of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, you won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're cooking up some foolish plan with that low-grade brain of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to steal Kaiba Corporation,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will completely\N destroy your ambition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Steal Kaiba Corporation?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.38,0:17:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That guy only has\N one Monster on the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am a little worried\N about that set card...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.51,0:17:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But the manly Jounouchi never backs down from a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Rocket Warrior in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Are ya scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This match is done!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use my three Monsters to beat the crap outta your weak Wall Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.68,0:17:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll smash you with a Direct Attack, winning me the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.97,0:17:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Gearfried!\N Attack Holy Elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.79,0:17:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deck Master Ability, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, I forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a Deck Master Ability too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just how foolish can you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Deck Master Ability\N is perfect for someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.52,0:17:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Sentence!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.99,0:17:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Life sentence? What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.50,0:18:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sentence reversing victory by sacrificing 1000 Life Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It removes every Monster on your side of the field from the game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.34,0:18:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No way!? Just hold on!\N Is that even {\i1}possible{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.01,0:18:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but for every Monster I erase, the opponent takes 500 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.27,0:18:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means... I had 3 Monsters erased.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I lose 1500 Life Points?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You calculate well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But it's nothing to\N really worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that guy only\N has 200 of his Life left...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's an easy win.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pitfall of Hades...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.63,0:18:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can destroy any Monster Normal Summoned, Reverse Flip Summoned or Special Summoned Monsters
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with 1500 or greater Attack Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.78,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a Trap Card that\N removes them from play.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I assume that he'll use Holy Elf as a sacrifice to Summon a stronger Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.87,0:19:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll just have to spring this Trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.05,0:19:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.74,0:19:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cover one reverse card,\N then end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.78,0:19:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, look! There's a door over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.03,0:19:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.88,0:19:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouch-{\i1}kun{\i0}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Yugi, Anzu, you guys alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.59,0:19:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.63,0:19:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observers, go and sit\N in the spectator seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys arrived just at the right time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stay over there and admire the moment that I beat this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lets resume the Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.44,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouch-kun doesn't have any Monsters on the field...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's his opponent's turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will he be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the\N Magic-Type Black Curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I open my reverse card! Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By fusing Holy Elf\N and Magic-Type Dark Curtain,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.20,0:20:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon the Chaos Wizard!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.45,0:20:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By Summoning that Monster,\N you fell right into my trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}1300 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If his Attack Power isn't at least 1500, the Trap Card won't activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.24,0:20:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then activate the Magic Card, Plea of Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.52,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This lets any Level 4 or lower Fusion Monster I control attack in the turn they are Fusion Summoned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Wizard, Direct Attack the player Katsuya Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.93,0:20:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Jounouchi!\N -Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plea of Darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:20:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's a Continuous Magic that also increases the player's Life Points by 800 whenever they attack with a Level 4 or lower Fusion Monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.65,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then place one card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect that guy\N to recover his Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.81,0:21:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It took so much effort to back him into a corner in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.11,0:21:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Judge Man's Deck Master Ability and the effects of his Continuous Magic Card, Jounouchi's in hot water!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tries to bet on his Gamble Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.31,0:21:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he fails every time, putting him in a dire pinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:22:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi starts to think luck is no longer on his side,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but isn't something\N strange going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.29,0:22:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.05,0:22:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Betting on Victory"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.59,0:22:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.77,0:22:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.84,0:22:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.99,0:22:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:23:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.91,0:23:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.72,0:23:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.50,0:23:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.48,0:23:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
